00:02:09,850 --> 00:02:14,090
what are some of the trends that we see in research.
目前在研究中发现的一些趋势

43
00:02:16,990 --> 00:02:18,120
Right now it seems that
目前看来

44
00:02:18,300 --> 00:02:21,200
if there's only one form of exercise that you do,
如果你只能做一种运动

45
00:02:21,690 --> 00:02:23,260
the best bank for the buck,
那么最佳选择

