the aerobic exercise,that's terrific.That's great.
有氧运动 那也很好

52
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:48,950
Twice a week,3 times of weight training is great,
一周两三次举动训练非常好

53
00:02:49,170 --> 00:02:51,820
especially as you get older.
尤其是年纪大了以后

54
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:54,760
That...Weight training contributes more.
举重训练更加有用

55
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,780
