除了一周做六天运动以外

99
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:17,060
two of them include full out sprinting,rest,
其中两天还会做全速短跑 休息

100
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,770
full out sprinting,rest.
全速短跑 休息

101
00:05:20,330 --> 00:05:23,230
And what they've shown was that even less time than 30 minutes,
研究表明即使没有做够30分钟

102
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,830
you can get the same effect,
但还能得到同等的效果

103
00:05:24,990 --> 00:05:28,120
the same psychological effect and even better.
同等的甚至更好的心理效果

104
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:33,520
What I do twice a week: I introduce interval training.
我一周也会做两次间歇运动

105
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,080
So for example,
所以 举个例子

106
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:38,230
this morning when I was on my trampoline,I did it for 30 minutes.
今天早上我在蹦床上跳了30分钟

107
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:41,850
And out of the 30 minutes,there were 4 sprints.
在这30分钟里 我还做了4个短跑

108
