I'll videotape it and I'll...Maybe not.Maybe not.
我下次拍下来 还是不要了

111
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:57,650
So 4 sessions of sprints,and I have my heart monitor on,
4次短跑 我戴着心率监测仪

112
00:05:57,930 --> 00:06:01,390
going all way- for me it's about 165 heart rate,
快速跑一段 我的心率大约是165

113
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:10,080
between 165 and 170,and then resting,going back to about 110,
165到170之间 然后休息 下降到110

114
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:12,500
which is less than 60 percent of my maximum,
少于我最大心率的60%

115
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,420
and then doing it four times.
如此重复四次

116
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,720
And for the rest of the 30 minutes,
这30分钟里其余的时间

117
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:19,410
I just do moderate aerobic exercise.
我只做缓和的有氧运动

118
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,620
So I also introduce the interval training.
所以我也做间歇运动

119
00:06:22,690 --> 00:06:25,870
The weight training I do less of,because I get that from Yoga-
举重训练就比较少做 因为我做瑜伽时

120
00:06:26,460 --> 00:06:28,880
a lot of the strengthening exercises.
就有这种加强体能的效果

121
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:32,570
The most important thing though that
但最重要的一点是

122
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:34,330
I do want to say about interval training
我想说 间歇运动

123
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:36,860
is that, especially for perfectionists,
特别是对于完美主义者来说

124
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:38,470
it's very easy to over-train.
很容易导致训练过度

125
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:41,250
You don't want to get to your maximum heart rate
大家最好不要达到最大心率

126
00:06:41,460 --> 00:06:44,130
and keep it there for a long time,even if you can.
并且持续一段长时间 即使你做得来

127
00:06:44,380 --> 00:06:46,640
More does not necessarily mean better.
更多并不意味着更好

128
00:06:46,930 --> 00:06:49,300
Again,unless you are training for Olympics,
再说一次 除非你是备战奥运

129
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:51,680
in which case you do want to get to
这种情况下有时你就要达到

130
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:55,270
100 percent of your maximum heart rate at times,
100%的最高心率

131
00:06:56,020 --> 00:06:58,410
for maximum health you want to get to 90 percent,
想练出最健康的身体 达到90%…

132
00:06:58,620 --> 00:07:01,710
maximum 95 percent of your maximum heart rate,
最大心率的95%就行了

133
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:04,790
which is why a heart rate monitor can help so much.
所以戴上心率监测仪就很有用

134
00:07:05,330 --> 00:07:08,340
Because it can tell you when you are working too hard
因为它能告诉你 运动是否强度太大

135
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:10,360
or when it's too easy.
或者强度不足

136
00:07:13,910 --> 00:07:16,060
Bottom line: variety is good for exercise.
总之 换换花样有助于运动

137
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:18,520
If you can introduce dancing,it's great exercise.
你可以跳舞 这也是好运动

138
00:07:18,710 --> 00:07:21,670
