你可以 偶尔去健身室健身

139
00:07:21,830 --> 00:07:23,620
once in a while playing basketball,
偶尔打篮球

140
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:27,120
rowing- the more variety,the better.
划艇 花样越多越好

141
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:31,270
But the foundation: at least we,ideally 4 times a week,
只要保证 至少对我们来说 一周四次

142
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,470
30 minutes of aerobic exercise.
一次30分钟的有氧运动

143
00:07:35,890 --> 00:07:38,440
So we stopped last time with overcoming barriers.
上节课我们讲到克服障碍

144
00:07:39,170 --> 00:07:41,250
