and to have distracters,such as TV,and your MP3,
用一些东西分散注意力 例如电视 MP3

154
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:10,760
and whatever it is.
能分散注意力就行了

155
00:08:12,290 --> 00:08:13,980
Another barrier- and this one is,
另一个障碍

156
