00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:41,850
So they get not enough,but more exercise,
所以他们运动得更多 虽然还是不够

165
00:08:42,690 --> 00:08:44,950
whereas one of the first things that go in college,
但是我们读大学第一件放弃的事

166
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:50,710
especially or only for students who do not play on the team,
尤其是那些不参加团队活动的学生

167
