all the colors seem so much brighter.
所有颜色都变得鲜艳多了

499
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:42,080
The world seems so much clear.
整个世界似乎都变得更明亮了

500
00:28:43,380 --> 00:28:50,940
And I say to myself,"wow.I must've become enlightened."
我心里想"我肯定觉悟了"

501
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:54,490
Because I read in books and I heard people talking about it
因为我在书上看过有人说

502
00:28:54,670 --> 00:28:57,320
that when you become enlightened,everything becomes clear.
当你觉悟时 一切事物都变得明亮

503
00:28:57,490 --> 00:29:00,900
The world becomes even more beautiful than it already is.
世界变得比原来更美了

504
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:05,230
And I were sitting there on the sofa,
我坐在沙发上

505
00:29:05,460 --> 00:29:10,620
and just admiring the strong colors,
欣赏着鲜艳的颜色

506
00:29:10,820 --> 00:29:13,900
the beauty,the clarity of every thing.
美景 明亮的世界

507
00:29:14,090 --> 00:29:16,100
And I said to myself,"after so many years"-
我心想"经过这么多年"

508
00:29:16,270 --> 00:29:18,170
I've been meditating for over ten years,
我冥想了十年了

509
00:29:18,360 --> 00:29:21,880
"after so many years,I'm finally enlightened."
"经过这么多年 我终于觉悟了"

510
00:29:22,980 --> 00:29:24,450
And I started to act differently,
我的行为举止开始变了

511
00:29:24,610 --> 00:29:25,850
because you know enlightened people
因为觉悟了的人

512
00:29:26,040 --> 00:29:28,630
don't go around telling people they are enlightened.
不会到处告诉别人他们觉悟了

513
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:30,000
Well,this is an exception.
这节课是一个例外

514
00:29:30,170 --> 00:29:32,620
But...So I didn't tell anyone.
但…我没有告诉别人

515
00:29:32,780 --> 00:29:35,590
I didn't even tell Tammy that I'm enlightened.
我甚至没有告诉Tammy我觉悟了

516
00:29:35,760 --> 00:29:39,450
But I was walking on air and the next day,the next morning,
第二天早上 我步履轻盈了

517
