I would wake up and again my ritual observation on off
我醒来又开始我每天例行的看景

518
00:29:43,950 --> 00:29:46,970
the mountains in a distance and I said,
看着远处的山 我想

519
00:29:47,150 --> 00:29:52,300
"wow.The world is so beautiful.I'm enlightened."
"世界太美丽了 我觉悟了"

