00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:26,150
And she said,"you know I haven't been able to get out there.
她说"我一直都够不着窗外

528
00:30:26,180 --> 00:30:26,770
But I got this machine.
但我买了一个机器

529
00:30:26,900 --> 00:30:30,170
You know the two side machine with a,with a magnet.
一个有两边的机器 有一块磁铁的

530
00:30:30,340 --> 00:30:34,130
I was finally able to get it.And I finally cleaned the window."
我终于买到这个机器 把窗擦干净了"

531
00:30:34,760 --> 00:30:36,290
So much for my enlightenment.
我的觉悟原来是一场空欢喜

