00:30:37,240 --> 00:30:42,150
So you know,maybe there is enlightenment- I don't know.
也许真的有觉悟这回事 我也不知道

533
00:30:43,060 --> 00:30:45,910
But the key with meditation is not about reaching that stage,
但冥想的关键并不是达到这种境界

534
00:30:46,100 --> 00:30:47,740
when everything suddenly becomes so clear.
看到一切都变明亮了

535
00:30:47,950 --> 00:30:50,430
