要想这样 把窗户擦干净可能更快

536
00:30:50,860 --> 00:30:53,950
But that's not what meditation is about.
但觉悟不是冥想的目的

537
00:30:54,650 --> 00:30:58,560
Meditation is about being present,being in the here and now,
冥想是专注于现状 此时此刻

538
00:30:58,750 --> 00:31:01,300
struggling with being in the here and now.
与此时此刻的存在作挣扎

539
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:05,160
And when we lose our thought,
当我们思想涣散了

540
00:31:05,380 --> 00:31:09,020
when we lose our focus on the breath,simply bring it back.
当我们对呼吸分心了 集中回来就行了

541
00:31:09,750 --> 00:31:12,320
That is the practice- losing it and bringing it back.
这就是冥想 分心 集中

542
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:13,940
Losing it and bringing it back.
分心 集中

543
00:31:14,140 --> 00:31:17,420
