The meditators,people who have been doing it for many years,
那些练习冥想很多年的冥想者

563
00:32:12,550 --> 00:32:13,870
for a very long time.
练习了很久的人

564
00:32:14,270 --> 00:32:18,460
And what they asked,the researchers like Richie Davidson,
这些研究者包括Richie Davidson

565
00:32:18,670 --> 00:32:19,910
University of Wisconsin,
任职于威斯康星大学

566
00:32:20,950 --> 00:32:26,920
Jon Kabat-Zinn from University of Worcester,
伍斯特大学的Jon Kabat-Zinn

567
00:32:27,150 --> 00:32:29,000
people like Herbert Benson,
像Herbert Benson这样的人

