他们会很难生起气来

641
00:36:22,710 --> 00:36:26,640
even if the topic was upset,personally upsetting to them,
即使这个话题很容易让他们生气

642
00:36:26,870 --> 00:36:29,920
such as scientists arguing about the existence of God.
例如科学家争论上帝是否存在

643
00:36:30,210 --> 00:36:32,290
And they said,"I couldn't get upset."
他们说"我生不起气来"

644
00:36:32,940 --> 00:36:37,220
Because calm is contagious,just like happiness is.
因为平静是会传染的 就是快乐会传染一样

