1081
01:02:22,900 --> 01:02:31,190
So sit comfortably in your seats as much as possible.
大家尽可能舒服地坐在座位上

1082
01:02:31,420 --> 01:02:31,930
Your back straight,
后背挺直

1083
01:02:32,090 --> 01:02:35,790
leaning on the back if that is more comfortable.
如果背靠着椅子更舒服的话 就靠吧

1084
01:02:39,570 --> 01:02:42,400
Elongate your neck as much as possible.
把脖子尽量伸长

1085
01:02:43,090 --> 01:02:46,000
Create a straight line in your upper body.
上半身形成一条直线

1086
01:02:46,630 --> 01:02:51,380
Plant your feet as comfortably as you can on the floor.
把脚尽量舒服地放在地板上

1087
01:02:52,050 --> 01:02:55,160
If there's a cross and you feel uncomfortable,uncross them.
如果觉得交叉着腿不舒服的 就放下来

1088
01:02:55,860 --> 01:03:02,860
And rest your hands either on your legs
可以把你的手放在腿上

1089
01:03:03,320 --> 01:03:06,140
or fold it however you feel comfortable.
也可以合起来 你觉得舒服就行了

1090
01:03:08,130 --> 01:03:11,080
And if you feel comfortable,close your eyes.
如果你觉得闭上眼睛舒服的 就闭上

1091
01:03:24,460 --> 01:03:25,920
Wherever your attention is now,
不管现在你的注意力在哪里

1092
01:03:26,120 --> 01:03:31,290
wherever your focus is now,bring it to your breath.
都把它集中在你的呼吸上

1093
01:03:33,370 --> 01:03:39,320
Breathe deeply into your belly
深深地吸进腹部

1094
01:03:41,300 --> 01:03:46,470
and then breathe slowly,gently,gracefully out.
然后慢慢地轻轻地呼出来

1095
01:03:51,700 --> 01:03:59,520
Take a deep breath and slow,gentle,quiet exhalation.
深吸一口气 慢慢地轻轻地呼出来

1096
01:04:00,110 --> 01:04:03,030
And repeat this a few times.
重复几次

1097
01:04:18,080 --> 01:04:19,640
If your mind wanders,
如果你精神分散了

1098
01:04:19,850 --> 01:04:25,390
simply,gently bring it back to the breath and practice.
慢慢把它集中回呼吸和练习上就行了

1099
01:04:46,400 --> 01:04:50,430
As you continue to breathe,shift your attention,
一边呼吸 一边转移你的注意力

1100
01:04:50,640 --> 01:04:53,240
your focus to your body-
转移到你的身体上

1101
01:04:58,920 --> 01:05:09,630
your feet,shins,your legs,your wrist,your belly,your back.
你的脚 小腿 腿 手腕 腹部 背

1102
01:05:09,810 --> 01:05:17,040
Just scan your whole body- your chest,neck,your head.
扫描你全身 你的胸膛 脖子 头

1103
01:05:17,990 --> 01:05:23,920
And find one area in your body that is slightly tense,
找出你身体感到微微紧张的地方

