observe the tension.
观察这股紧张感

1109
01:05:44,400 --> 01:05:50,530
Just observe and accept it is.
观察它 接受它

1110
01:05:56,650 --> 01:05:59,080
Continue to breathe deeply
继续一边深呼吸

1111
01:05:59,300 --> 01:06:02,290
as you are observing that part of the body.
一边观察这个身体部位

1112
01:06:03,600 --> 01:06:05,580
And just look how interesting it is.
看看这多有趣

1113
01:06:08,150 --> 01:06:10,100
That you have that sensation there.
你那个部位有这样一个感觉

1114
01:06:12,630 --> 01:06:16,950
With each breath,embrace it.
每呼吸一次 就接受它

1115
01:06:19,350 --> 01:06:20,790
There's nothing right;
你的感觉

