1135
01:09:12,510 --> 01:09:14,890
Take another deep breath in.
再深吸一口气

1136
01:09:15,620 --> 01:09:20,510
Slow,gentle,quiet exhalation.
慢慢地轻轻地呼出来

1137
01:09:35,920 --> 01:09:41,750
